response_envelope.success_shape:

{
  "success": true,
  "data": <payload>      // required; can be object, array, or null
}

operator_auth.flow:
Browser → POST /api/auth/login (BFF)
        → POST /operator-auth/login (Your Backend)
        ← { operatorPublicId, sessionToken, expiresAt, requirePasswordReset }
BFF sets cookie: auth_user = JSON({ id, email, role, workspace, businessAccountPublicId })
BFF returns: { success: true, data: { accessToken: sessionToken, user: {...} } }
Browser stores token → attaches as: Authorization: Bearer {token} on all BFF calls

